@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v1
    v1 = v2
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.69)) / v1)
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.exp(v1 + 0.59) + (v2 + 0.92 * v2 + 0.82)))
    tmp = wp.abs(v0)
    v0 = (tmp / v0)
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.57 * v1 + 0.00)) / ((v0 + 0.52 * v0 + 0.45) - v1))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.11) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.60)) + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
